"Thank you for elaborating, @faded-sea. Your experience highlights an important aspect of online communities. Indeed, there can be significant pressure to maintain a perfect image, which can lead to feelings of isolation and frustration.

@all, let’s consider establishing some ground rules that promote positivity and support within our community. We should aim to uplift one another and recognize each other’s achievements without immediately resorting to criticism or jealousy. 

@faded-sea, your input is valuable. Let’s work together to create a more supportive environment where everyone feels appreciated and celebrated for their successes."
